Class AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation

  • java.lang.Object

    public class AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation
extends Object
implements AccessibleDisplay
    The AccessibleDisplayScreenReaderImplementation class is official implementation of AccessibleDisplay interface for screen readers.
